    },
    {
      "message": "refactor: refactor graph_request handling in BasicNode logic\n\n- Add `graph_user_message` as an optional field to `BasicLLMRequest`\n- Update the path to `graph_user_message` in `BasicNode` to access it from `config[\"configurable\"][\"graph_request\"]`\n- Modify `BasicNode` to set `graph_user_message` on the request object instead of updating it directly in the `config` dictionary\n\nSigned-off-by: umaru <15875339926@139.com>",
