      "message": "refactor: simplify message processing by removing filtering logic\n\n- Simplify the processing of human messages by removing keyword-based filtering logic and directly formatting messages for display.\n- Remove logic for identifying \"internal process\" messages, simplifying their treatment within the system.\n- Delete keyword-based logic for identifying and prioritizing computational content.\n- Remove unnecessary checks for technical message filtering in the `_extract_meaningful_content` function, enabling more straightforward content extraction.\n- Delete the `_is_internal_process_message` and `_is_obvious_technical_message` helper functions, consolidating logic and reducing complexity.\n\nSigned-off-by: umaru <15875339926@139.com>",
